布朗大學是美國的頂尖大學之一，2005年[[美國全國經濟研究所|美國全國經濟研究所]]按高中生[[顯示性偏好|顯示性偏好]]將其排在全美第7位，<ref>{{cite web |url=http://papers.ssrn.com/sol3/papers.cfm?abstract_id=601105 |title=SSRN-A Revealed Preference Ranking of U.S. Colleges and Universities by Christopher Avery, Mark Glickman, Caroline Hoxby, Andrew Metrick |publisher=Papers.ssrn.com |accessdate=2010-02-22 |archive-date=2015-10-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151017145723/http://papers.ssrn.com/sol3/papers.cfm?abstract_id=601105 |dead-url=no }}</ref> 此外因為有眾多的[[羅德獎學金|羅德獎學金]]、[[杜魯門獎學金|杜魯門獎學金]]、[[馬歇爾獎學金|馬歇爾獎學金]]、[[蓋茨獎學金|蓋茨獎學金]]得主而列在[[新聞週刊|新聞週刊]]/[[每日野獸|每日野獸]]的“美國聰明人士最多學校”（America's Brainiac Schools）中第5位。<ref>{{cite web|title=America's Brainiac Colleges|url=http://www.thedailybeast.com/newsweek/features/college-rankings/2011/brainiacs.all.html|publisher=The Daily Beast|accessdate=2012-01-28|archive-url=https://archive.is/20120919152303/www.thedailybeast.com/newsweek/features/college-rankings/2011/brainiacs.all.html|archive-date=2012-09-19|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

